<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
    <meta charset = "UTF-8">
    <meta name = "viewport" content = "width=device-width, height=device-height, initial-scale=1">
    <style type="text/css">
  <title>회원가입 화면</title>
#wap{width : 1250px; height : 940px;}
#content{width : 1250px; height : 900px;}
#footer{width : 1250px; height : 70px;}
#signup_form{background-color: white;}

.
/* 회원가입 영역 */
  .signup_header{}
  .signup_header h1{font-family : Arial; color :#353535; padding-top: 60px; padding-bottom: 40px;
                          font-size : 39px; text-align: center;}

.signup_content{text-align: center;}
.signup_content .signup{}
.signup_content .signup .id_field .form-control {width:350px; height: 60px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding-left: 9px; font-size: 15px;
  border-radius: 3px; border : solid 1px #4C4C4C;}
.signup_content .signup .pw_field .form-control{width: 350px; height: 60px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding-left: 9px; font-size: 15px;
  border-radius: 3px; border : solid 1px  #4C4C4C;}
.signup_content .signup .name_field .form-control{width: 350px; height: 60px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding-left: 9px; font-size: 15px;
  border-radius: 3px; border : solid 1px  #4C4C4C;}
.signup_content .signup .email_field .form-control{width: 350px; height: 60px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding-left: 9px;  color : #747474; font-size: 13px;
    border-radius: 3px; border : solid 1px   #4C4C4C;}
.signup_content .signup .btn btn-warning btn-lg{width : 357px; height : 60px; margin-top: 10px;
       background-color: #E5A102; color : white; font-size: 20px; border-style: none;
     border-radius: 3px;}
.signup_content h2{font-size: 15px; color : #4C4C4C;}

 /* footer */
 .footer{ font-size: 12px; text-align :center; display: block; border-top: solid 1px #D5D5D5;}
 .footer li{display : inline; padding : 0px 0px 20px 20px;}
 .footer li a{text-decoration: none; color : black;}

  </style>
  </head>

<body>
  <div class = "container">
      <div class = "col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-3">
          
          <h1><span class = "fa fa-sign-in"></span></h1>
      
          <!-- 인증 처리 후 메시지가 있으면 메시지 표시 -->
          <% if (message.length > 0) { %>
              <div class = "alert alert-danger"><%= message %></div>
          <% } %>
    
          <form action = "/signup" method = "post" >
  <div id= "wap">
  <div id = "content">
    <div id = "signup_form">
  <div class = "signup_header">
    <h1>회원가입</h1>
  </div>

  <div class = "signup_content">
    <div class = "signup">
    
<div class = "form-group">        
<div class ="email_field">
  <h2 class = "signup_tit"><label for ="email" >이메일</label></h2>
  <input type = "text" name = "email" class="form-control" id="email" />
</div>
</div>
<div class = "form-group">
<div class = "pw_field">
  <h2 class = "signup_tit"><label for="pw">비밀번호</label></h2>
  <input type = "password" name = "password" id= "pw" class = "form-control"/>
</div>
</div>
<div class = "form-group">        
<div class = "name_field">
   <h2 class = "signup_tit"><label for ="nickname">닉네임</label></h2>
   <input type = "text" id= "nickname" name = "nickname" class= "form-control"/>
</div>
</div>    

<div>
<p>
    <button type = "submit" class = "btn btn-warning btn-lg">회원가입</button>
</p>
</div>
    
        
    <hr>
    <p>이미 계정이 있으신가요? <a href = "/login">로그인하기</a></p>
    <p><a href = "/">홈으로</a></p>    
  </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<div id = "footer">
<div class = "container">
<div class = "footer">
<ul>
  <li><a href ="#">사이트 도움말</a></li>
  <li><a href ="#">사이트 이용약관</a></li>
  <li><a href ="#">사이트 운영규칙</a></li>
  <li><a href = "#">개인정보</a></li>
</ul>
<address>
  Copyright&copy;wap5.co.kr All Right Rederved
</address>
</div>
    </div>
</div>
</div>
</form>
              
</div>
    </div>
    </body>
</html>
